#Turtle Racing Game
A fun and interactive Python turtle racing game where you can bet on which colored turtle will win the race!

🎮 Game Description
This is a simple yet entertaining racing game built with Python's turtle graphics module. Five colorful turtles compete in a race across the screen, and you get to predict which one will win!

✨ Features
Interactive Betting System - Place your bet on which turtle you think will win
5 Colorful Racers - Red, Blue, Green, Yellow, and Purple turtles
Random Movement - Each turtle moves forward by a random distance (0-10 units) per turn
Win/Lose Detection - Automatically detects the winner and tells you if you won or lost
Visual Racing - Watch the turtles race in real-time across the screen
